      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just watching a movie of my life. like i’m not even the one living it. i look in the mirror and i don't recognize the person looking back, it's just a shell performing all the tasks i'm supposed to do. i don't think there's anything actually left inside anymore.",
