    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s not really about finding inspiration though. that’s just more performing. i look at the crowd, i look at my friends, and i just feel... absent. like if i just stopped showing up, if i just stopped the act entirely, nobody would even notice the real me was gone because i was never really there to begin with. it feels like the performance is the only thing keeping a void from being visible.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
